type=\"hidden\" name=\"locale\" value=\"en-gb\" id=\"locale\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"js\" value=\"1\" id=\"js\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"css\" value=\"1\" id=\"css\"> <button class=\"s-b-button\" aria-live=\"polite\" aria-labelledby=\"sb1-label\" type=\"submit\" tabindex=\"\" aria-pressed=\"false\" id=\"sb1\"> <span class=\"s-b-icon s-b-s\"> <i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"gelicon gelicon--share s-b-gelicon\"></i> </span>  <span id=\"sb1-label\" class=\"s-b-labels\"> <span class=\"s-b-label s-b-s\" role=\"presentation\">Share</span> <span class=\"s-b-label-long s-b-s\" role=\"presentation\">this page</span> <span class=\"s-b-hidden\" role=\"presentation\">This page has been Shared 34 times</span> </span> </button> </form> </span> <span class=\"s-b-panel  s-b-p-auto\" id=\"sb1-panel\" data-variant=\"light\"> <span class=\"s-b-pointer\"></span> <p>Share this with</p> <ul class=\"s-b-p-networks\">  <li> <a href=\"http://digg.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fguides%2Fzcvdhyc&title=How%20did%20Britain%20let%20250%2C000%20underage%20soldiers%20fight%20in%20WW1%3F&bodytext=Greg%20James%20asks%20how%20we%20allowed%20so%20many%20underage%20soldiers%20to%20fight%20in%20WW1.%20Was%20it%20the%20eager%20boys%20themselves%20or%20a%20society%20that%20encouraged%20them%20to%20fight%3F\" target=\"_blank\" data-window-width=\"900\" data-window-height=\"560\" data-network=\"digg\" tabindex=\"\" class=\"s-b-p-a\"> <span> <i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"gelicon gelicon--digg\"></i> </span> Digg  </a> </li>  <li> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fguides%2Fzcvdhyc\" target=\"_blank\" data-window-width=\"626\" data-window-height=\"236\" data-network=\"facebook\" tabindex=\"\" class=\"s-b-p-a\"> <span> <i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"gelicon gelicon--facebook\"></i> </span> Facebook  </a> </li>  <li> <a href=\"https://plus.google.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fguides%2Fzcvdhyc\" target=\"_blank\" data-windo