mty.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01qhmty\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"k-g-sprite icon k-article\">Read</span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">History</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">BBC News: The youngest WW1 soldier</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-2 iwonder\n                    k-colour-palette-palette-2\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/guides/z3kgjxs\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp square\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x256/p01ld0d8.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01ld0d8\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><span class=\"genre k-type-body-index\">History</span><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-header\">How did so many soldiers survive the trenches?</p></div><div class=\"connection\"><p class=\"k-type-body-index\"><img src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/80x80/p01l1wrw.jpg\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"type\">Presented by</span><span class=\"name\">Dan Snow</span></p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-3 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p01p33cd\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01snr02.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01snr02\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Remembering soldiers from across Britain &amp; Ireland</p></div></a></div><div class=\"\n                k-promo promo-4 gel\"><a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/ww1\"><div class=\"media\"><img class=\"resp widescreen\" src=\"http://ichef.bbci.co.uk/images/ic/256x144/p01snhcq.jpg\" data-pid=\"p01snhcq\" alt=\"\"><span class=\"\"></span><span class=\"overlay\"></span></div><div class=\"context\"><p class=\"title\n                            k-type-sub-header\">Discover new perspectives on World War One</p></div></a